OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,FDonald Campbell's legendary Bluebird
OL,7,FK7 hydroplane returned to Coniston
OL,8,FWater for the first time in nearly 70
OL,9,Fyears last week - but the highly-
OL,10,Fanticipated event was not without its
OL,11,Fdisappointments.
OL,13,FIt had been rumoured that Bluebird
OL,14,Fcould reach speeds of up to 150mph
OL,15,Fduring the week-long festival, but one
OL,16,Fjaunt at 100mph was the hydroplane's
OL,17,Fonly dalliance with high speeds.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
