OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779376271
OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,FOver the course of the week thousands
OL,7,Fof spectators gathered around Coniston
OL,8,FWater, but not all left feeling
OL,9,Fsatisfied.
OL,11,FIt was only on Friday that Bluebird
OL,12,Ffinally got 'on its plane', which
OL,13,Fmeans the craft went fast enough to
OL,14,Fenable it to skim across the surface
OL,15,Fof the water, taking advantage of the
OL,16,Flaws of hydrodynamics.
OL,18,FUntil then, K7 had only been on slow
OL,19,F'familiarisation runs' on Coniston
OL,20,FWater, with poor weather and technical
OL,21,Fissues scuppering hopes of more.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
