FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779376271
OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,FHer pilot for the week was Australian
OL,7,FDave Warby, whose father set the
OL,8,Fcurrent world water-speed record in
OL,9,F1978.
OL,11,FAfter reaching 100mph in Bluebird,
OL,12,FWarby said: "K7 is the boat that
OL,13,Finspired my father to break the world
OL,14,Fwater-speed record.
OL,16,F"It's a very surreal moment. I'd like
OL,17,Fto thank the people for their
OL,18,Fpatience, it's been a hard week
OL,19,Fgetting the boat sorted out."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
