PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779376271
OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,FStrong winds prevented any attempts on
OL,7,FTuesday, the second day of the
OL,8,Ffestival, while on Wednesday and
OL,9,FThursday Bluebird required technical
OL,10,Fwork and what the festival organisers
OL,11,Fdescribed as "a few more adjustments".
OL,13,FOn that day an announcement was made,
OL,14,Fsaying: "It obviously needs some extra
OL,15,Fadjustment. The engineers thought they
OL,16,Fhad done enough, but obviously a
OL,17,Flittle more is required.
OL,19,F"She's very nearly there. It's not
OL,20,Fsomething you can do with a Swiss army
OL,21,Fknife."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
