PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779376271
OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,FThe final days of the Bluebird K7
OL,7,Ffestival were similarly plagued by
OL,8,Fproblems.
OL,10,FWind and waves scuppered hopes for a
OL,11,Ffast run on Saturday, and that evening
OL,12,Fthe team revealed a "bent catch on the
OL,13,Fcanopy" needed repairing.
OL,15,FAt that time, Donald Campbell's
OL,16,Fdaughter Gina told ITV Border: "As
OL,17,F(pilot) Dave Warby said to me, if it
OL,18,Fwas that easy, everybody would be
OL,19,Fdoing it. That is the crux of it.
OL,26,@yD@ApmyD@Gpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779376271
OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,F"She's an old lady, she's got a new
OL,7,Fheart, and her new heart needed to be
OL,8,Ftweaked, and she was getting a bit of
OL,9,Ffuel starvation."
OL,11,FOn Sunday, meanwhile, reserve pilot DJ
OL,12,FGibbs was supposed to make his debut
OL,13,Fin Bluebird K7, but an issue with the
OL,14,Fstarter hose delayed the launch. Poor
OL,15,Fweather later meant a run was called
OL,16,Foff - with organisers saying it would
OL,17,Fhave been too unsafe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779376271
OL,3,CBluebird K7 festival: Triumph and
OL,4,Cdisappointment at Coniston Water
OL,6,FJeff Carroll from the Ruskin Museum,
OL,7,Fwhich will house Bluebird in a
OL,8,Fspecially constructed annex, said:
OL,9,F"It's a lesson that these things
OL,10,Faren't exact sciences.
OL,12,F"Sometimes what you think is going to
OL,13,Fwork doesn't, so you're left there
OL,14,Fscratching your head looking for the
OL,15,Fsolution."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
